  "summary": "0316.HK shows a mild positive short-horizon volume drift and a strongly positive recent residual versus weekday baselines (last week volumes materially above typical levels). After shrinking for high residual noise/possible event-driven regime effects, the bounded multiplicative update scale for next-session volume is estimated at ~1.106x versus the anchor (weekday) baseline.",
